ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009832520b20ecf4f9779a7daad12e2483aa06a0","tid":415582,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地幾時講過要人權 有黨就夠啦"},{"pid":"69ad6f4b3a794dd6106f81bbb2a109985c766dc8","tid":415582,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得單新聞假假地"},{"pid":"89493aea2e2b3f32614af3a8dcdb49e42d93dd58","tid":415582,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得單新聞假假地</blockquote><br />\n都唔係第1單啦<br />\nRTHK都有報上訪同截訪連殺人都有<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 高鐵上面可以搞假新聞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸人都冇你咁冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16c1256c24ea6cfa5c46b6af322624fd99a5095","tid":415582,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd191a9d03213016681950c9b30d928d4c208954","tid":415582,"uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:50:08.000Z","msg":"有曾看過動物也有人權的嗎？沒有。"},{"pid":"87327df4350ee30444bae08826d2cd4442d67af7","tid":415582,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"所有五毛 藍屍奶共者等畜生想唔想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd531126746fb24325f1b68ad3e7d9b4f42ff2b0","tid":415582,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:54:21.000